OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy, perhaps some
OL,6,Fbright spells, and a few showers.
OL,7,FThese will be mostly light and this
OL,8,Fafternoon, although there is a chance
OL,9,Fof isolated heavy showers.
OL,10,FTemperatures slightly lower than
OL,11,Fprevious days, but still warm.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FScattered showers, a few
OL,14,Fperhaps heavy at first, will fade away
OL,15,Fthis evening to leave a dry night with
OL,16,Foften large amounts of cloud but also
OL,17,Fsome clear spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
