OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FGenerally dry and fine, with
OL,6,Fjust a small chance of isolated
OL,7,Fthunderstorms developing. Temperatures
OL,8,Fclimbing, becoming very warm and humid
OL,9,Finland although onshore breezes will
OL,10,Fkeep coastal areas cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FPredominantly dry and becoming hot or
OL,14,Fvery hot, with the heat peaking
OL,15,FTuesday. Humid and very warm nights.
OL,16,FChance of occasional low cloud along
OL,17,Fthe coast, and isolated thunderstorms
OL,18,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
